data.text: Have you heard? US Airways and TAM will be leaving the Star Alliance network in March. Further info here: http://t.co/qJ4Z50m3Ge

@DEBKANCHAN @malvikakapoor8 Our hub is in Seoul, Korea!
@uhgatubud Hope you have a wonderful flight to NGO!

@TheNiteshRao Thank you!
@akashbagdiya We love to fly with people who love traveling!

@42nandoah Keep warm and happy snow day!
@yamnedboh1260 Hope you stay warm and dry!

@Ian_N7919G Thanks for sharing the photo with us!

@Sugandih They're not the Business Smartium seats, but we do offer Premium Business Class seats.
@airlineguys Thanks! Hope you have a great week!
@DanSparx Thanks! Will you be flying with us again any time soon?
@junkieaircraft Not yet, but soon! We'll keep you posted when the time comes.

Happy Friday! Have you seen our A380's first test flight yet? Here's a great video to get you inspired! http://t.co/pjBltvFIYt #TGIF

Happy Friday! Are you ready for a relaxing weekend? #FirstSuite http://t.co/QgWcurS3DS

@ShaneyHwang Wow! We hope you're able to stay warm somehow!
Are you fighting through the snow storm? Share with us your photos of the #snow!

Hey Asiana Club members! You may be eligible for health benefits and discounts on airfare when you visit Seoul: http://t.co/tu0xEqaLL8
Don't forget to check your flight status here: http://t.co/02xnqQpw1X. JFK is facing some delays due to snow. http://t.co/k2AlHTko1A
@abustamanteg ...Or send an e-mail to usasianaclub[at]http://t.co/I44HUkMKFg to get exact details for claiming missing @StarAlliance miles.
@abustamanteg Hi, if you're an Asiana Club member you'll need to contact our AC service dept for further instructions. (800)227-4262
RT @garethseltzer: Big marks to @AsianaAirlines for great service & basically double beds! Great flying! http://t.co/MHgKXW8VWk
Winter storms may affect your flights to/from JFK & ORD. Be sure to check our webpage to keep up with your schedule: http://t.co/02xnqQpw1X
Seoul would be the perfect place to see them! RT @heatherw19752: my dream is to go to Seoul next April during Cherry Blossom festivals
@ArielleFreytag We're told the winners will be listed on our webpage sometime tomorrow. (Jan. 22nd, Korea time)
@Rochelle1291 Sorry~ Following!
We're sending a DM to the concert poster winners today, so check your Twitter inboxes!
@Soo_Bri Congrats on your graduation and good luck! We hope your travel dreams come true :)
@shiningtaomint You're welcome, and good luck!
@Swasian It's always a pleasure to visit the Motherland. Good luck and we hope your travel dreams come true!
@butterfli253 Maybe you can dream to fly our #FirstSuite someday, too! http://t.co/oSeIhGnbb4
@melanie_0925 Asian food is quite delicious, we agree! :) We hope your dreams come true.
We'd like to know what your travel dreams are. Tweet us! #IHaveADream #MLKDay2014
@Rochelle1291 Thanks for following! Now you'll have to wait for us to announce the winners. Good luck!
@42nandoah Thank you for your loyalty and support! Good luck!
@nessar00 Thank you and good luck!
@larlyssafay Welcome aboard! We can't wait to have you on board. Good luck on the #UKISS signed poster event!
@InuKa2004 Thanks for participating. Good luck!
@theOGdHo Looks like you'll need to fly Business or First every time from here on out! Thanks for coming on board with us.
"If u can't fly then run, if u can't run then walk, if u can't walk then crawl, but whatever u do u have to keep moving forward." #MLK
Happy Monday and #MLKDay, tweeps! Traveling doesn't take a break today. What are your travel plans?

RT @carlousmoochous: @AsianaAirlines @Boeing #777 landing @SydneyAirport #AvGeek http://t.co/OigpIbNPRY

@TheWindowSuite @lufthansa Welcome aboard! Have a great flight!
Here's a Boeing-sized smile to brighten up your day. #HappyHumpDay! http://t.co/COEwLp2jr9

“There are no foreign lands. It is the traveler only who is foreign.” – Robert Louis Stevenson #TravelQuotes
@Sayak234 @Kevinwoo91 @u_kisseli Good to know you enjoyed the show! We hope your first concert was a blast! :)
RT @arachmanto: Quite amazed by @AsianaAirlines in flight meal. Incheon-Jakarta i got tasty Bibimbab & Burito. #2014Travel http://t.co/cVUu…
Happy Monday, Tweeps! We hope you had a restful weekend. What are your travel plans for the week?
